82
00:04:34,910 --> 00:04:35,710
Like you shouldn't give up eating

83
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:36,960
for fear of choking.

84
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:39,430
You were betrayed once,

85
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,800
then you trust no one now?

86
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:42,280
What are you going to do

87
00:04:42,470 --> 00:04:43,750
for the rest of your life?

88
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:56,400
Hey, what are you doing?

89
00:04:56,710 --> 00:04:57,360
You deserve it.

90
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:58,240
I'm getting payback.

91
00:04:59,910 --> 00:05:01,430
Are you childish or what?

92
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:03,080
Weren't you just scolding me
a moment ago?

93
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:04,630
I scolded you...

94
00:05:05,910 --> 00:05:07,120
I apologize to you now.

95
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:07,910
Is that okay?

96
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:09,960
You are annoying.

97
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:18,520
Alright.

98
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,680
Since you did that to me,

99
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,000
you should come with me
to the work party.

100
00:05:24,150 --> 00:05:24,960
With so many pals

101
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,240
and Mr. Chen,

102
00:05:27,470 --> 00:05:27,910
I don't believe

103
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,400
there's no one worth trusting.

104
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,430
Put it to the spicy pot.

105
00:05:41,710 --> 00:05:42,430
Yeah, the spicy one.

106
00:05:42,710 --> 00:05:43,240
Have some more.

107
00:05:43,590 --> 00:05:44,680
Easy, easy.

108
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,160
Here, take some.

109
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:55,160
