113
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,920
Hand out these red packets to everyone.

114
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,040
Bye.

115
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:36,720
Hurry.

116
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,040
Fifteen.

117
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,070
Everybody, listen up.

118
00:06:41,070 --> 00:06:41,560
Listen ,everyone.

119
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:42,630
Boss is here.

120
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:43,630
- Hi, boss.
- Hi, boss.

121
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:44,360
Hello, boss.

122
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,240
Here, I just want to

123
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,360
express my gratitude to everyone

124
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,310
for the hustle and hard work

125
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:51,070
this past year.

126
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,160
I'm truly thankful for

127
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,070
for all of you.

128
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,190
I see all the hard work

129
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:56,870
and dedication

130
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:58,120
you put in.

131
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,240
We'll be on break

132
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:01,270
for Lunar New Year break

133
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,720
starting tomorrow and continuing
until the Lantern Festival day.

134
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,510
During the New Year vacation,

135
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,240
I wish you a lot of joy

136
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,070
and a fantastic time!

137
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,070
- Yeah!
- Great!

138
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:13,920
And also,

139
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:16,070
our big boss Mr. Qi

140
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:17,390
couldn't make it today.

141
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,310
but he sends his regards.

142
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,120
He wanted each of you

143
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,510
to have

144
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:24,720
a red packet!

145
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,360
Here,

146
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,720
take it.

147
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:28,510
Thanks big boss.

148
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,390
- Thanks.
- Thank you.

149
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:30,830
Take it.

150
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:31,390
Thank you, boss.

151
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,560
Here, Xiaoyuan.

152
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,310
Take one yourself.

153
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,720
OK. Great.

154
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:36,600
So,

155
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:39,160
what we need to do today

156
00:07:39,750 --> 00:07:42,480
is have a great time!

157
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,240
- Cheers!
- Yay!

158
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,240
Let's all raise a toast

159
00:07:44,310 --> 00:07:45,120
to the boss together!

160
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:45,560
Come on.

161
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,720
Three, two, one.

162
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,920
Thank you, boss.

163
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,310
Come on, boss.

164
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:00,750
Go on.

165
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:01,600
Raise your glass, boss.

166
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:04,870
Here.

167
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,430
OK, you can switch.

168
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:20,270
Xiaoyuan,

169
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,360
I have something to tell you.

170
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:25,720
I won't be working at the salon

171
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,270
after the vacation.

172
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,480
Why?

173
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:33,600
I'll stay in my hometown
and get married.

174
00:08:38,310 --> 00:08:38,870
You can't let go of

175
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:40,360
the rich man's fortune,

176
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:42,310
so you've decided to
devote yourself to the family?

177
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,630
My parents fell ill.

178
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:51,950
They are ill.

179
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:54,390
I have to take care of them.

180
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,830
The family land

181
00:08:56,950 --> 00:08:58,040
lies fallow.

182
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,800
Without farming,

183
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,070
there's even less income.

184
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:04,800
Only...

185
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,190
Only if I get back and settle down,

186
00:09:09,310 --> 00:09:10,480
can I take care of them

187
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,430
and earn money.

188
00:09:18,430 --> 00:09:20,190
I thought you like doing hairdressing.

189
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,310
Sure.

190
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,560
I really like it.

191
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,480
I've put in so much effort

192
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,600
learning hairdressing,

193
00:09:29,310 --> 00:09:30,560
how could I not like it?

194
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:33,830
But I won't be able to do it

195
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,430
after I go back.

196
00:09:43,190 --> 00:09:43,720
Xiaoyuan,

197
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,870
Please don't be like me.

198
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,000
You must

199
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,720
stick to your dreams.

200
00:09:54,430 --> 00:09:55,160
Honestly,

201
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,310
I always remember

202
00:09:58,630 --> 00:09:59,510
that day

203
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:01,120
when you stood up for me.

204
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,630
I deeply regret

205
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,390
what I've done to you

206
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,550
because of my fear and weakness.

207
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,360
Xiaoyuan,

208
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:17,670
you're so cool

209
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,080
and brave.

210
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,240
Unlike me,

211
00:10:22,550 --> 00:10:23,670
always hesitating,

212
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:26,870
and unable to accomplish anything.

213
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:31,120
You should hold onto that

214
00:10:31,870 --> 00:10:33,000
and move forward.

215
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,670
Fulfill your dreams

216
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,750
without regrets.

217
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:51,680
[Fashion Hairdressing Salon]

218
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,630
Xiaoyuan?

219
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,000
You are still here.

220
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:27,550
I'll go home tomorrow,

221
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:28,720
what about you?

222
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:30,550
I...

223
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:32,510
When?

224
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,270
Don't you go home for Spring Festival?

225
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,870
Perhaps I can stay
and take care of the salon.

226
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:38,910
Forget about it.

227
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:39,960
Let you stay?

228
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:40,840
I don't think so.

229
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,120
Go get your train ticket.

230
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,150
Your Grandma is waiting for you.

231
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:44,960
I don't go.

232
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,240
Hey,

233
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:47,790
it's the Lunar New Year.

234
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:48,750
You're not going home?

235
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,360
What about your family reunion dinner?

236
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,840
I spent the New Year alone these years.

237
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:54,120
Buy a ticket,

238
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,480
head to the beach for some sun,

239
00:12:56,270 --> 00:12:57,360
chill for a week,

240
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:58,550
and then return.

241
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:02,000
I guess your year-end bonus

242
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,320
is running out.

243
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,200
How can you afford that?

244
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,200
Unless you won the lottery.

245
00:13:08,630 --> 00:13:09,270
By the way,

246
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:11,390
haven't you stopped talking

247
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:12,120
to Qi Lian?

248
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:13,320
He'll stay here

249
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,600
during the vacation.

250
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,320
If you insist on staying,

251
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:17,720
I can ask him to drop off

252
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,720
some New Year's Eve dinner

253
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:19,600
and dumplings for you.

254
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:20,910
You want me to do that for you?

255
00:13:22,910 --> 00:13:23,960
I'm not avoiding him.

256
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:26,320
I just don't want to see him.

257
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,120
Please, listen to me.

258
00:13:33,030 --> 00:13:34,720
The conflict between two people

259
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:35,840
often arises because

260
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,150
they feel each other's actions

261
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,960
don't meet their expectations.

262
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,960
So they'll misunderstand each other,

263
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,390
each believing they are in the right.

264
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:43,080
Am I right?

265
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:46,790
So, right from the start,

266
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:47,320
I shouldn't have

267
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,600
too many expectations.

268
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:50,750
In the end,

269
00:13:51,790 --> 00:13:53,670
we can only help ourselves.

270
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:56,360
But if that's the case,

271
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,270
does it mean

272
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:58,630
there are no emotional bonds
between people?

273
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,320
That's fine.

274
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,390
Then we don't need to help each other?

275
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,320
No one is meant to help anyone else.

276
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,840
Can you do it?

277
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:10,910
Don't let Qi Lian help you?

278
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,630
For one thing,

279
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:13,840
you can work here

280
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,550
is also thanks to

281
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:15,790
Qi Lian helping you

282
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,840
take care of

283
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:17,360
your grandma, right?

284
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,120
He is not helping me.

285
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:20,480
You know,

286
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,080
he's been busy

287
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,200
assisting the police

288
00:14:23,390 --> 00:14:24,630
with the case.

289
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,360
Isn't that helping you?

290
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,120
You don't need his help.

291
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,670
Can you do this all by your own?

292
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:32,080
For people,

293
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:34,240
not everything is clear-cut.

294
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,670
You like him,

295
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:38,200
